sections.verses:
Mangalaa Aaratee Karata Modita Mana, Ura Antara Aananda Bharee…Tek

Tanakee Aaratee Tatva Pancha Mukha, Eenhdri Ekaadasha Baatee Karee;
Toopa Prakruti Bhinhjaaee Bateeyanh, Brahma Agnise Jyota Jaree…..Mangalaa…1

Chittavana Chandana Chaitana Arachana, Anubhava Shankha Liyo Samaree;
Adhudhu Sabda Agama Agochara, Sad Guru Kahata Pokaara Karee…..Mangalaa…2

Agrabattee Vairaaga Visheshana, Prema Pushpa Dharyo Haara Hari;
Gyaan Ghadi Yaalee Giraajana Kaarana, Loka Chaturdasha Khabara Paree…..Mangalaa…3

Laksha Niraajana Neerakhata Nishadina, Pati Sanaatana Bhaava Bharee;
Kahe Kuver Aaise Hariku, Tana Mana Sahita Raho Samaree…..Mangalaa…4

Aaratee Mahaaraaj Raaja Kee, Mangala Manoratha Bhaava Bharee;
Agra Kapoora Sugandha Sohaavata, Baatee Ekaadasha Agyna Jaree…Tek

Bhaala Tilaka Kesharako Jyunh Raaje, Chammara Shira Para Chhatra Dharee;
Kausatubh Mani Ura Tanta Hee Shobhaa, Nijaananda Ghanashyaama Hari…..Aaratee…1

Baajintra Bahu Vidha Vidha Baaje, Nigama Vade Yasha Heja Karee;
Shaarada Sura Sameepa Saba Thaade, Aja Bhava Shree Pati Soorata Dharee…..Aaratee…2 

Santa Sajjana Jana Triyaa Saba Thaade, Atakee Soorata Kara Yugala Joree;
Kiye Utpanna Ansha Aapa Yunh Jaanee, Drashta Karunaa Sarva Para Pasaree…..Aaratee…3

Daasa Narana Aaratee Keeje, Reejha Pada Raja Adhikaaree;
Sarvaateeta Eesha Pada Sabake, Soee Prabhu Khele Jana Sanga Hari…..Aaratee…4
